Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:18.73,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要唤出情感之名 则无休无止无穷无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:26.82,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神传来呼唤 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:28.66,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相随
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:29.91,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:33.49,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无论光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:37.37,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如紧凑相连的拼图零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:41.63,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:45.88,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:50.55,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}终将指引我们走向所坚信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:57.31,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤诚真心 逐步升温
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:23:01.15,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无虚情假意 非利益所趋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:05.90,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真实自我
